{"tid":2503743,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"櫻花樹下嘅食物質素真係需要改善","createTime":"2021-04-25T10:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T15:47:59.000Z","uid":309524,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"71572f1c35c83737d879f07673ee6f89635cb11a","tid":2503743,"uid":309524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都淨係食黃店，上個星期揸車入天水圍樂湖見呢間嘢，見係黃店就諗住試下，就叫咗個吉列豬扒拉麵，個friend就叫咗個肥牛拉麵，一咬落舊豬扒度 啲粉勁厚，味道又唔係特別好食，明明叫豬骨湯底，唔知點解有浸酸味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n食過一次真係不了，希望櫻花樹下老細見到可以考慮吓點樣改善佢哋嘅食物質素，因為真係好撚難食啊屌你老母，如果你哋再唔改善，好快執笠，如果啲人覺得龍門好難食，我夠膽講，佢哋一定未食過櫻花樹下"},{"pid":"0d3f07bf09471c9e7f3e78319f50211ab3b76451","tid":2503743,"uid":50502,"like":6,"dislike":48,"score":-42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"黃店不嬲出名難食 好食既十間先得一兩間"},{"pid":"efc1c1d7e48d1c3cabafbb78f4813342e7b59207","tid":2503743,"uid":309524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d3f07bf09471c9e7f3e78319f50211ab3b76451","tid":2503743,"uid":50502,"like":6,"dislike":48,"score":-42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"黃店不嬲出名難食 好食既十間先得一兩間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"但依間真係好撚差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd54f5877fe2af070998998d704a6625631a8fa","tid":2503743,"uid":11598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:23:48.000Z","msg":"佢啲飯先過癮 懷疑唔識煮飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a83f5226d3c649160578ba0e827115ac555eb1","tid":2503743,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"去隔離食焗飯啦<br />\n幾好食"},{"pid":"84dc52104ac1051ef9ebda76a1559647ae892b2e","tid":2503743,"uid":32657,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"61a83f5226d3c649160578ba0e827115ac555eb1",